----

| state |  button | action | signalling |
|-------|---------|--------|------------|
| connected, connecting | long press 2 | disconnect & start scanning | no signalling |
| scanning | long press 2 | delete bond #1, start pairing #1 | blink |
| connected | hold 1 + press 2 (x1, x2, x3) | select profile | blink
| any | long press 1 | start SPI | blink
